plot: As the forces of evil mass, the Doctor, Yaz and Dan face perilous journeys and seemingly insurmountable obstacles in their quest for survival.

While the Doctor confronts her mother between universes old and new, Yaz, Dan, and Jericho travel to Nepal in 1904 to find out when and where the final battle for Earth will occur. In 2021, Kate Lethbridge-Stewart discovers who has been pulling the strings to render Earth defenseless against an alien invasion.—Gislef
